[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Bible Adventures
	]em
	" is a collection of three platformer games in one. Each game is (very loosely) based on a story from the Bible. Gameplay itself has very little biblical connection.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		[b 
			"Noah's Ark
		]b
		" - Noah collects animals and food in preparation for the flood.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		[b 
			"Baby Moses
		]b
		" - Moses' mother must carry baby Moses past Egyptian guards, spiders, and birds to reach a safe place to put him in the Nile.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		[b 
			"David & Goliath
		]b
		" - David must first gather sheep that have wandered off, then he can go to battle against Goliath.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
